Embedded_text: ViVidCanvas, Mio: So... Everyone, it's nice to meet you. I'm ViVidCanvas's leader, Mio Serizawa.
ViVidCanvas, Mio: Excuse the intrusion! It's been a while, Aya-san, Maya-san!
ViVidCanvas, Serina: It's all thanks to Aya-san, for giving us lots of opportunities to interact! You gave us a big helping hand!
